      "settings": {
        "eyebrow": "Our story",
        "title": "Where culture meets curation",
        "intro": "<p>Presha Trends was built for people who care about product, story and trust in equal measure. We approach luxury streetwear and rare sneakers with a curator's eye and a resale standard that respects the culture.</p>",
        "panel_label": "Position",
        "panel_title": "A Dubai-based point of view on global street luxury",
        "panel_text": "<p>Presha Trends sits at the intersection of fashion, rarity and confidence. We are building more than a storefront. We are building a destination for curated product, trusted authentication and a sharper luxury resale experience.</p>",
