        "panel_pill_two": "Luxury streetwear",
        "chapter_eyebrow": "What drives us",
        "chapter_title": "Presha is built around trust, taste and cultural clarity",
        "chapter_text": "<p>In luxury resale, product matters, but context matters just as much. We care about how an item fits into culture, why it deserves attention and how it reaches the customer with confidence still intact.</p><p>That is why Presha Trends focuses on selection, presentation and verification with equal discipline. We want the experience to feel elevated from the first click to the final delivery.</p>",
